Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.21,0:01:09.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  邮递员
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:09.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, mailman
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, see you tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.05,0:01:14.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,信来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:14.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The mail's here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.08,0:01:15.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:15.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you get?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.09,0:01:18.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:18.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有本杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A magazine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:24.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(430.816,205)}奢华生活文摘
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.22,0:01:21.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是奇怪  我不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:21.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's funny, I don't remember
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.79,0:01:24.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己有订过奢华生活文摘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:24.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,subscribing to Fancy Living Digest
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.89,0:01:28.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看这书里光鲜亮丽地描绘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:28.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at these glossy depictions
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.77,0:01:30.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更高级的生活标准
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:30.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of a higher standard of living
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.82,0:01:32.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位已经富到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:32.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This guy's so rich
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.10,0:01:34.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都有个游泳池中池了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:34.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he has a swimming pool in his swimming pool
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.62,0:01:36.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位还有鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:36.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This guy's got shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.65,0:01:37.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:37.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.95,0:01:39.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷我邮件是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:39.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stealing my mail, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.75,0:01:42.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们应该庆幸我没有去举报了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:42.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're lucky I don't report you to the authorities
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.12,0:01:43.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:43.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.06,0:01:45.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那杂志里的阔佬是怎么弄到钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:45.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how do those people get all that money?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们是创业家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're entrepreneurs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.21,0:01:48.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,专门卖东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:48.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They sell things to people
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.92,0:01:50.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卖的哪种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:50.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What kind of things?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.28,0:01:51.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:51.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.29,0:01:52.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正是大家想买的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:52.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Things people want to buy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.92,0:01:54.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别乱动我的邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:54.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, keep your paws off my mail
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.42,0:01:55.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:55.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.62,0:01:57.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得去当创业家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:57.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got to become entrepreneurs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.98,0:01:59.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会伤着我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:01:59.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that gonna hurt?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.30,0:02:00.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  快直接回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:00.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, Patrick, without thinking
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.78,0:02:03.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你现在要啥就有啥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:03.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you could have anything in the world right now
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.34,0:02:04.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:04.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what would it be?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.48,0:02:06.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要再来点想问题的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:06.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More time for thinking
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.98,0:02:07.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  要实在的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:07.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, something real
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要物件  可以付钱买的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,an item, something you would pay for
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.98,0:02:11.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力棒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:11.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A chocolate bar?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.23,0:02:12.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是好点子  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:12.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.72,0:02:14.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就来当巧克力棒上门推销员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:14.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll be traveling chocolate bar salesmen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:18.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(571.407,211.001)}便宜货超市
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.82,0:02:17.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奢华生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:17.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fancy living
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here we come
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.11,0:02:23.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给这两个撞业家让条道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:23.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make way for a couple of "entrepe-nooers"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick, this is it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.64,0:02:27.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们奢华生活之路的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:27.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the first step on our road to living fancy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.70,0:02:28.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我来就行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:28.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just follow my lead
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.71,0:02:32.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下午好  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:32.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.11,0:02:35.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有没有兴趣要来点巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:35.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could we interest you in some chocolate?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.38,0:02:36.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:36.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chocolate?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是不是说了  巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you say "chocolate"?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.49,0:02:40.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对的  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:40.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.50,0:02:42.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要加果仁的还是不加果仁的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:42.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With or without nuts?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.18,0:02:43.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:43.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chocolate?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.72,0:02:44.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:44.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chocolate?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.10,0:02:49.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:49.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chocolate
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chocolate
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.52,0:02:53.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:53.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chocolate
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.73,0:02:55.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚那第一位不算
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:55.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, that first guy didn't count
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.43,0:02:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才是我们真正的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is our real first step
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.50,0:02:58.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:58.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.77,0:03:00.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要买点巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:03:00.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you like to buy some chocolate?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.95,0:03:02.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是巧克力棒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:02.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chocolate bars, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.52,0:03:04.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  我们是巧克力棒推销员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:04.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, we are chocolate bar salesmen
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看你们俩推销员做得还挺一般
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A couple a mediocre salesmen, if you ask me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.89,0:03:10.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样运送商品是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:10.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's no way to carry your merchandise
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行不行  那样错了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.32,0:03:15.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们想当优良推销员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:15.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys want to be good salesmen, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Most certainly sir
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要是有点自尊的巧克力棒推销员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, no self-respecting candy bar salesman
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.63,0:03:23.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都会带上这种玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:23.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would be caught dead without one of these
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.01,0:03:25.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:25.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.99,0:03:28.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是巧克力棒袋  你们两个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:28.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a candy bar bag, you knucklehead
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.52,0:03:30.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,精心特制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:30.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's specially designed
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.02,0:03:33.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,且有丝绒内衬  舒适安放每条巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:33.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to cradle each candy bar in velvet-lined comfort
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.29,0:03:33.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:33.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直是浪费我时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm wasting my time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.93,0:03:36.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们用不着袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:36.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't need these bags
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need them
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你们卖得愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy hunting
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Suckers
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.04,0:03:52.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奢华生活  我们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:52.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fancy living, here we come
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,试下下一家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's try next door
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.13,0:04:00.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:00.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.09,0:04:05.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是卖我们巧克力棒袋的那位吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, weren't you the same guy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who sold us these candy bar bags?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.22,0:04:06.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:06.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't recall
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过看样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it looks to me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.12,0:04:10.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们俩身上袋子还挺多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:10.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like you fellas have got a lot of bags there
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个少女杀手可聪明了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two lady-killers are too smart to be
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须要有我专利认证的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without one of my patented
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力棒袋收纳用袋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,candy bar bag carrying bags
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.52,0:04:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要买二十个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll take 20
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.94,0:04:24.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们俩好心年轻人要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:24.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What can I do for you two nice young men?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.57,0:04:25.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在卖巧克力棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:25.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're selling chocolate bars
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.94,0:04:27.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要买一根吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:27.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like to buy one?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.12,0:04:29.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听起来好像还挺好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:29.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds heavenly
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要买一根
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take one
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一根巧克力棒马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One chocolate bar coming up
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定就在里面的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know they're in here somewhere
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.04,0:04:56.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没空陪你们闹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:56.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have time for this
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.48,0:04:58.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:58.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力棒卖给漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One chocolate bar for the nice
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.77,0:05:01.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:01.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chocolate
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.07,0:05:01.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:01.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lady
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.55,0:05:06.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:06.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chocolate
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:08.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(822.466,603)}小餐馆
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们表现不太好啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not doing so well, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.63,0:05:09.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得要换个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:09.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need a new approach
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.95,0:05:11.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,换个策略
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:11.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a new tactic
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.83,0:05:12.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:12.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.50,0:05:13.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来裸奔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:13.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's get naked
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.50,0:05:16.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  等卖房再裸奔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:16.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, let's save that for when we're selling real estate
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.37,0:05:17.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定有门道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:17.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There must be something
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,之前为什么要买那些袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was the reason we bought those bags?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说我们一般
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He said we were mediocre
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.67,0:05:22.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:22.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他让我们觉得特别了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He made us feel special
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.83,0:05:25.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  确实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:25.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he did
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我回去再买点袋子来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to buy more bags
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.10,0:05:27.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先别走  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:27.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不我们试下友善待人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't we try being nice?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讨好顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,flatter the customer
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.38,0:05:37.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他自我感觉良好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:37.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make him feel good
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.90,0:05:39.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:39.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.98,0:05:45.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好像做得有点过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:45.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You laid it on a teensy thick there, old pal
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.56,0:05:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me try
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.20,0:05:48.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:48.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.80,0:05:49.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:49.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go away
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你近来如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How ya doin'?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我近来如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How am I doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.41,0:05:55.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要买点巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:55.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wanna buy some chocolate?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.41,0:05:56.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讨好到人家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:56.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got him now
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  巧克力含糖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, chocolate has sugar
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(777,920)}起 泡
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,糖会转化成发胖的脂肪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and sugar turns to bubbling fat
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.18,0:06:01.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不对啊  爱吃巧克力的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:01.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, lover boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It tickles
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们也看得出来我不碰巧克力了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As you can see, me and chocolate no longer hang
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(472.993,151)}十三岁的我
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.09,0:06:08.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照片一张五块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:08.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can keep that for five bucks
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要买十张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take ten
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连一根巧克力棒都没有卖出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We haven't sold one chocolate bar
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.85,0:06:15.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉我们太容易分心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:15.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling we're too easily distracted
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们现在来约定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's make a pact right now
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到下一家要专心推销
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that we will stay focused on selling at the next house
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.15,0:06:21.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:21.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.81,0:06:23.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,握手约定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:23.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's shake on it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.73,0:06:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚刚有说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.12,0:06:27.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星别忘了  专心看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:27.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember, Patrick, focus
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.24,0:06:29.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:29.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.91,0:06:30.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下午好  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:30.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在卖巧克力棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're selling chocolate bars
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这胖子怎么在盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is Chubby here staring at me?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,专心看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Focusing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我滚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back up, Jack
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.26,0:06:48.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这家还真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:48.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice place you got here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不明白哪里做错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't understand what we're doing wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.43,0:06:54.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么都明白不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:54.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't understand anything
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,推销这行肯定还有别的什么秘诀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There must be something to this selling game
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.82,0:06:58.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只有咱不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:58.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that we're just not getting
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别人就都懂  比方看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Other people do it, I mean, look at that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(308.3,805.001)}快吃藤壶薯片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1127.752,799)}美味可口
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.82,0:07:03.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快吃藤壶薯片  美味可口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:03.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Eat Barnacle Chips, they're delicious"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.64,0:07:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半难吃死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They are most certainly not delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.60,0:07:07.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用我的吃法就好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:07.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not the way I use them
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果这薯片一天能卖好几百万包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yet they sell millions of bags a day
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.24,0:07:11.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能不搞夸张的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:11.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe if they didn't stretch the truth
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就卖不了这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they wouldn't sell as many
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.82,0:07:14.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:14.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得搞夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to stretch the truth
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chocolate
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起合作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll work as a team
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来给这客人预热预热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me get this customer warmed up
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.94,0:07:24.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后你来把这家拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:24.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then you come in for the kill
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The kill
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  年轻的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, young lady
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在卖巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're selling chocolate
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你妈在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is your mother home?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.02,0:07:38.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:38.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.64,0:07:40.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:40.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫什么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's all that yelling?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.23,0:07:46.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就等不及要我去死  是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:46.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just can't wait for me to die, can you?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.68,0:07:48.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们在卖巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:48.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're selling chocolate
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.15,0:07:48.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:48.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chocolate?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.94,0:07:49.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:49.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.57,0:07:50.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:50.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.19,0:07:51.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在卖什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:51.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are they selling?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.31,0:07:52.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:52.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chocolates
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.86,0:07:53.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卖什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:53.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.52,0:07:54.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:54.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chocolates
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不清
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.01,0:07:57.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们在卖巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:57.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're selling chocolates
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.92,0:07:59.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们在卖巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:07:59.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're selling chocolate?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.36,0:07:59.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:07:59.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chocolate?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.18,0:08:04.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还记得巧克力刚发明出来那会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:04.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I remember when they first invented chocolate
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.88,0:08:07.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那甜甜的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:07.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet, sweet chocolate
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我向来都恨死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always hated it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.84,0:08:12.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可这种巧克力不是用来吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:12.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But this chocolate's not for eating
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是用来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's for
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.34,0:08:14.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要把它涂在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:14.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You rub it on your skin
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.84,0:08:17.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就能长生不老了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:17.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it makes you live forever
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.26,0:08:18.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别别别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:18.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.55,0:08:20.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说长生不老吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:20.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Live forever, you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我买了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take one
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  懒惰鬼玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, you lazy Mary
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.98,0:08:28.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快把那巧克力涂我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:28.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Start rubbing me with that chocolate
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.57,0:08:30.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我恨你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:30.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是继续搞夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If we keep exaggerating the truth
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就能有奢华生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we'll be fancy-living in no time
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说谎万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray for lying
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以让你长头发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll make your hair grow
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.91,0:08:40.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:40.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.86,0:08:42.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我老婆就想要长胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:42.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My wife's trying to grow a beard
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.61,0:08:44.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以让你言语谈吐变聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:44.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll make you sound smart
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.00,0:08:46.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要买二十块
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:46.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take 20
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以让你脸不再变丑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll keep your face from getting any uglier
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.95,0:08:50.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:50.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just in time
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.33,0:08:51.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以让你飞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:51.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They make you fly
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.66,0:08:52.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以让你恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:52.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll fall in love
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以给世界带来和平
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They'll bring world peace
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以让你穿墙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll walk through walls
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.38,0:08:57.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以让你统治世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:57.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll rule the world
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这回说的谎肯定最强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This'll be the best lie yet
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.87,0:09:05.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:05.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位一定会特别同情我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This guy will feel so sorry for us
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后就把咱所有巧克力都买走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he'll have to buy all of our chocolate
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.15,0:09:12.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们有什么事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:12.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What can I do for you boys?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想要买巧克力棒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would you like to buy a chocolate bar?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.69,0:09:16.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要做手术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:16.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need an operation
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.07,0:09:16.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:16.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同病相怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Small world
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.38,0:09:20.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:20.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you guys?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.33,0:09:24.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们有头部外伤跟内出血
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:24.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got some head trauma and internal bleeding
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有些家伙就是运气好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some guys have all the luck
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.29,0:09:30.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我生来就有易碎的骨头跟柔弱的皮肤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:30.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was born with glass bones and paper skin
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.25,0:09:31.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每天早上我都会断腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:31.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every morning I break my legs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.25,0:09:34.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每天下午我都会断胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:34.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and every afternoon I break my arms
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上  我疼得睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At night I lie awake in agony
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直至心脏病让我昏迷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until my heart attacks put me to sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.76,0:09:39.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:39.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  咱们快帮帮人家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, Patrick, let's help him
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.55,0:09:50.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:50.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Careful
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.44,0:09:51.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轻轻放下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:51.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put him down gently
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.40,0:09:56.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:56.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor, poor man
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If there's anything
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.48,0:09:58.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎样都行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:09:58.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,anything
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能帮得上你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can do to help you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.93,0:10:01.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有一样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:01.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There is one thing
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.82,0:10:03.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们也想象得到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:03.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As you can well imagine
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的医疗费特别的高
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my medical bills are extremely high
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过幸好  我活命的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but luckily I'm able to keep myself alive
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.96,0:10:08.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是卖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:08.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by selling
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.17,0:10:10.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:10.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,chocolate bars
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是心善
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Such nice boys
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下我心里可真是舒坦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It does my heart good
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.80,0:10:23.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,骗到了这两个顶级白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:23.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to con a couple of class-A sucker-roonies like those two
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先别误会  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然能救他一命是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's great that we helped him out
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.02,0:10:34.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是镇上已经没几个买巧克力的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:34.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but there's no one left in town to sell chocolate bars to
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,认了吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's face it, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.96,0:10:40.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是废物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:40.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're failures
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can live with that
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.28,0:10:46.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还是改名叫何苦兄弟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:46.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's change our names to "Why" and "Bother"
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.71,0:10:50.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:50.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chocolate
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  别伤害我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, don't hurt us
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.97,0:10:53.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.51,0:10:57.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:57.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.89,0:11:01.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一整天都可想着要逮着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:11:01.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to catch you boys all day
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.49,0:11:04.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然我逮着你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:04.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that I've got you right where I want you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想买下你们所有的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to buy all your chocolate
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢您的惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patronage
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们过上奢华生活了吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are we living the fancy life yet, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没呢  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not yet, pally
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先得把钱都花掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First we got to spend all the money
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.74,0:11:25.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可要先把钱花在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:25.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what are we going to spend it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(647.729,225)}奢华
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.46,0:11:30.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上好  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:30.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good evening, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.74,0:11:32.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来张单人桌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:32.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Table for one, please
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  整间餐厅已经租给了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but the whole restaurant has been rented
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.11,0:11:36.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一家私人聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:36.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to a private party
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.42,0:11:39.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我只有今晚才能放纵奢华啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:39.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's my only night to be fancy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.55,0:11:42.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁这么有钱  能租下来一整间餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:42.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who could afford to rent out the whole restaurant?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.55,0:11:45.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是对富创业家  以及他们的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:45.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A couple of rich entrepreneurs and their dates
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.35,0:11:49.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么  你们两位小姐认识多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:49.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, how long have you two ladies known each other?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.48,0:11:51.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:51.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:56.57,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(397,396)}美人鱼战士\N{\fs38.25} \N{\fs150.75}和企鹅男孩\N{\fs38.25} \N{\fs150.75}5
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:58.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.15\pos(294.144,439)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:58.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.15\pos(506.144,809)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:12:00.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1083.822,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.15\pos(406.144,335)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:02.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.15\pos(288.144,423)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:02.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.15\pos(482.144,723)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:02.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1023.17,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.51\pos(242.045,361)}客串
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.51\pos(930.045,587)}配音 美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.51\pos(1018.045,887)}配音 企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.95,0:12:08.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩的全新冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:08.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The New Adventures of Mermaidman and Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.43,0:12:09.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在熟悉的一家餐厅里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:09.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In a familiar restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.95,0:12:11.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在熟悉的小镇一角里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:11.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in a familiar part of town
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:14.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(531.238,441)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.62,0:12:14.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发出了沮丧的呼声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:14.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a call goes out in frustration
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.22,0:12:15.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能给我快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:15.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you hurry up?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这呼声通常能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A call that would normally
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.13,0:12:20.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被裤头村的半退休守护者所回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:20.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,be answered by Bikini Bottom's semiretired champions
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.92,0:12:24.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除非他们就是引起问题的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:24.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If they weren't the ones causing the problem
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.09,0:12:25.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要一份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:25.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want a
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.55,0:12:27.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:27.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.69,0:12:28.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要一份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:28.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:31.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(742.129,110.999)}菜单
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.02,0:12:31.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:31.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.64,0:12:36.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生  能不能赶紧点餐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:36.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sir, will you please order already?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.23,0:12:37.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害整条队都不动了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:37.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're holding up the line
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士  来份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mermaidman, get a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've made my decision
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.99,0:12:49.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我来份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:49.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty for me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.02,0:12:51.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给这小朋友来份儿童堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:51.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a Pip-squeak Patty for the boy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给老子等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, wait just a darn minute
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不要儿童堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want a Pip-squeak Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.79,0:13:00.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要成人尺寸的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:00.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want an adult-sized Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.30,0:13:03.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡对你来说太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:03.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krabby Patty is too big for you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.07,0:13:04.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可吃不完
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:04.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never finish it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.78,0:13:06.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知不知道你这是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:06.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you see what you're doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.18,0:13:08.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是在把我当小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:08.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're treating me like a child
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.35,0:13:10.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友都是胃口大  肚子小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:10.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The boy's eyes are bigger than his stomach
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.85,0:13:13.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这也是问题所在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:13.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's another thing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.14,0:13:14.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:14.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not a boy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我老到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so old
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.69,0:13:18.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连老年斑上的皱纹都长毛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got hairs growing out of the wrinkles
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on my liver spots
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份儿童堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Pip-squeak Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有围兜跟高脚椅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And your bib and high chair
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.16,0:13:32.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老子68岁了  要蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:32.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm 68 years old and I want a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的儿童堡要冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your Pip-squeak is getting cold
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.71,0:13:35.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要我喂你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:35.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shall I feed you?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.82,0:13:37.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自个吃吧  死老头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:37.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feed this, old man
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经不想死死跟在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of playing second banana
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,某位胸罩男身后了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to a man who wears a bra
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.80,0:13:47.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从今往后要叫我企鹅男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:47.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From now on, I want to be called Barnacleman
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.55,0:13:52.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不保护不尊重我的民众了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:50.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm through with protecting citizens
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that don't respect me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我尊重你  企鹅男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I respect you, Barnacleman
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.25,0:13:56.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是企鹅男孩  我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:56.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's Barnacleboy, I
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.98,0:13:57.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:57.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean man
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.06,0:14:00.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:00.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget you people
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.73,0:14:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果不把我当英雄尊重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say if you're not going to give me any respect as a hero
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.15,0:14:07.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么只能把我当恶人尊重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:07.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then maybe you'll give me respect as a villain
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个恶人特别
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A villain who is
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,evil
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.66,0:14:12.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:12.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evil?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evil?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evil
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.81,0:14:22.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去投靠黑暗一方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:22.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm crossing over to the dark side
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.92,0:14:26.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我干嘛要浪费钱把整家店都照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:26.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why should I waste money lighting the whole store?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(752.169,323.001)}裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(746.144,789.001)}就要对你坏
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人说到邪恶了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did someone say "evil"?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的海上漏油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy oil spill
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩的夙敌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Mermaidman and Barnacleboy's arch enemies
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.85,0:14:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,射线恶魔和肮脏泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man Ray and the Dirty Bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.32,0:14:42.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安了  老山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:42.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nighty-night, you old goat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.44,0:14:46.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:46.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nighty-night
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能帮我盖被子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you tuck me in?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.59,0:14:52.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们打断你们悲惨又毫无意义的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:52.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We interrupt your bleak and meaningless lives
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:54.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(460.943,560.999)}新闻快报
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,插播本则特别报道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for this special news break
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,射线恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man Ray
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(718.025,213.001)}第一航海银行
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.12,0:14:58.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肮脏泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:58.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Dirty Bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.42,0:15:04.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有现在投靠黑暗一方的  企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:04.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, playing for the dark side, Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.63,0:15:06.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,企鹅男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:06.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacleman
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.05,0:15:09.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在裤头村犯下了一系列滔天大罪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have been committing a series of crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,throughout Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.68,0:15:17.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要抓到你们这些小屁孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:17.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get you crazy kids
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.77,0:15:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这三个人将他们新建的联盟命名作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These three have named their new alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:24.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(877,920)}柠 檬
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.62,0:15:24.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶人皆为大废物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:24.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every Villain Is Lemons
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亦作邪恶帮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,otherwise known as EVIL
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What can we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.44,0:15:31.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这场罪恶浪潮将何时停止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:31.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When will this crime wave end?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.93,0:15:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎样才能击败邪恶帮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How will we defeat the EVIL?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.40,0:15:37.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为什么要向你们问这些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:37.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why am I asking you all these questions?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.48,0:15:40.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:40.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman, where are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.12,0:15:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm right here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.83,0:15:46.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不必担心  良民们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:46.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, good citizens
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.35,0:15:52.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有东西会阻止我击败邪恶帮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:52.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nothing will stop me from defeating the EVIL
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.22,0:15:54.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:54.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.26,0:15:57.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:57.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:58.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(296.248,286.999)}冰淇淋
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.52,0:15:59.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:15:59.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.85,0:16:04.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来两球加麦麸粒的梅子味冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:04.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A double scoop of prune with bran sprinkles
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:09.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(842,800)}麸爆
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.07,0:16:13.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每次都害我拉肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:13.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goes right through me every time
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.28,0:16:15.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还是放弃吧  美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:15.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You might as well give up, Mermaidman
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们这边有三个  你那边只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's three of us and only one of you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.68,0:16:19.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没机会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:19.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't stand a chance
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没事吧  美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Mermaidman?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.04,0:16:26.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以你一个人的力量要怎么打败他们仨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:23.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are you going to beat
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all three of those guys by yourself?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.36,0:16:27.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:27.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.63,0:16:28.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:28.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I give up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't give up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来帮你怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What if we help you?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.38,0:16:34.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  这就是一馊主意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:34.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, that's a terrible idea
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.10,0:16:36.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那要是你们来帮我怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:36.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what if you help me?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.71,0:16:41.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么  谁想要拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:41.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, who wants to save the world?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.60,0:16:45.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:45.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.23,0:16:47.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要也得要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:47.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, you do
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.59,0:16:49.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世界没了就等于钱没了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:49.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No world means no money
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.58,0:16:52.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去拯救世界  不然开除你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:52.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, go save the world or you're fired
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.91,0:16:55.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:55.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then it's settled
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.21,0:16:57.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去美人鱼基地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:57.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the Mermalair
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.12,0:17:01.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼基地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:01.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Mermalair
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.25,0:17:05.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些衣服属于原版
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:05.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These costumes belonged to the original
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.43,0:17:09.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,国际超级老相识正义联盟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:07.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,International Justice League
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of Super Acquaintances
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.75,0:17:13.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正联是史上最英勇的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:13.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The I.J.L.S.A. were the most heroic heroes ever
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(697.941,131)}国际老相识正义联盟
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们正联也有史上最棒的午餐盒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you had the best lunch box, too
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.26,0:17:18.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一旦穿上这些衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:18.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once you put on these costumes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.38,0:17:22.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们的超能力就会归你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:22.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,their fantastic powers will become yours
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超能力不是这样起效的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't think super-powers worked that way
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.99,0:17:27.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:27.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.33,0:17:29.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超能力都蕴含在衣服里面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:29.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Power's all in the costume
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.26,0:17:32.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然干嘛要穿彩色内衣到处跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:32.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why else would we run around in colored undies?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.33,0:17:34.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒能想三个充分理由来解释了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:34.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can think of three good reasons
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞毛腿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Quickster
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.86,0:17:39.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超能力就是跑步速度非常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:39.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With the uncanny ability to run really
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.12,0:17:40.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:40.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,quick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.21,0:17:43.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要看我跑上那座山再跑回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:43.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Want to see me run to that mountain and back?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要看我再跑一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to see me do it again?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.48,0:17:47.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怒火船长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:47.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Captain Magma
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.11,0:17:49.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惹他生气  他就会爆发岩浆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:49.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get him angry and he's bound to erupt
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.89,0:17:51.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喀拉喀托大爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:51.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krakatoa
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弹性胖胖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Elastic Waistband
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.83,0:18:01.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能够把身体拉成各种神奇的形状
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:59.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Able to stretch his body
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:01.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,into fantastic shapes and forms
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我终于可以摸到脚趾头了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can finally touch my toes
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有无影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Miss Appear
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.10,0:18:11.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在看得到她  现在看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:11.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you see her, now you don't
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这身会不会显胖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does this outfit make me look fat?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.36,0:18:16.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,国际超级老相识正义联盟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The International Justice League
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:16.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of Super Acquaintances
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,维亚康姆的子公司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A subsidiary of Viacom
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.11,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 维亚康姆：《海绵宝宝》出品公司 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.28,0:18:20.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:20.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, it's agreed
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点一份奶酪匹萨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll get one cheese pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.49,0:18:25.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份辣香肠蘑菇匹萨  一份橄榄匹萨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:25.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one with pepperoni and mushrooms, and one with olives
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.92,0:18:28.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超级老相识们  请求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:28.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Super Acquaintances, we need your help
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.58,0:18:29.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的比目鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:29.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy halibut
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.79,0:18:30.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是首领
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:30.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's the Chief
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你介绍我  飞毛腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the introduction, Quickster
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是大伙儿都认得我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but we all know who Iam
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.52,0:18:39.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且重点是我们得知了邪恶帮的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:37.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More to the point, we've got news
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:39.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the whereabouts of EVIL
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.44,0:18:41.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行踪是个什么宗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:41.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The whoseabouts of what?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.36,0:18:43.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说出他们的位置就行  首领
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:43.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just tell us where they are, Chief
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.16,0:18:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会尽早把他们捆起来抓住的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:44.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we'll hog-tie them faster
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than you can say "salsa verde"
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.52,0:18:48.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们线人最近一次看到邪恶帮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:48.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our sources last saw EVIL
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.50,0:18:51.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在调情礁骚扰青少年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:51.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,harassing teenagers up at Make-Out Reef
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.33,0:18:52.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,调情礁就那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:52.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, Make-Out Reef
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.65,0:19:01.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的比目鱼啊  美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:01.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Floppin' flounder, Mermaidman
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.37,0:19:02.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,调情礁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:02.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make-Out Reef
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.24,0:19:03.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些恶魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:03.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those fiends
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.87,0:19:06.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然袭击荷尔蒙失调的小朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:06.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attacking hormonally stressed-out children
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,调情礁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make-Out Reef
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.95,0:19:11.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真尽兴  真尽兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:11.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good times, good times
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.60,0:19:13.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去调情礁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:13.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To Make-Out Reef
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Away
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.46,0:19:19.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以是不是吃不到匹萨了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:19.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does this mean we're not getting pizza?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1053.439,272.999)}悬崖危险
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.55,0:19:22.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:22.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.17,0:19:22.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要骚扰我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:22.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leave us alone
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.95,0:19:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别照了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, stop
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.47,0:19:24.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:24.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.47,0:19:29.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,约翰南茜坐树上  亲亲吻吻无处藏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:29.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,John and Nancy sitting in a tree, K-I-S-S-I-N-G
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用手电筒照那辆车  射线恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shine the flashlight in that car, Man Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With pleasure
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊  这样可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, man, that's not cool
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放过那些打情骂俏的小年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leave those young lovers alone
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.95,0:19:45.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是霉人鱼战士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:45.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Milkmaid Man
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.08,0:19:49.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用不着费劲找你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:49.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've saved us the trouble of tracking you down
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.25,0:19:51.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这些恶魔不会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:51.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You fiends can't win
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.46,0:19:52.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们人少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:52.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're outnumbered
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.46,0:19:54.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怕是糊涂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:54.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You senile bag of fish paste
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.72,0:19:57.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们这边有三个  你那边只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:57.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There are three of us and only one of you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,变两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make that two
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.88,0:20:02.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞毛腿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:02.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Quickster
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怒火船长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Captain Magma
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Four
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弹性胖胖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Elastic Waistband
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.27,0:20:15.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:15.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Five
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.06,0:20:17.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:17.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,M-M-Miss Appear?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.36,0:20:20.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加上我就是十个  吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:20.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And me makes ten, I think
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下情况不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't feel so good about this
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们形象的玩具要卖不出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There goes our toy deal
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.99,0:20:32.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超级老相识们  出击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Super Acquaintances, attack
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.12,0:20:33.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:33.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饶命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, mercy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喀拉喀托大爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krakatoa
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弄下来  弄下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get it off, get it off
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.13,0:20:46.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弄下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:46.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get it off
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.03,0:20:47.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来救你  飞毛腿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:47.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll save you, Quickster
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.51,0:20:48.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:48.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.69,0:21:01.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来给你冷却  飞毛腿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:01.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll cool you off, Quickster
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用我的水弹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with one of my water balls
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.37,0:21:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  不对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No-no, no-no
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是飞毛腿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not the Quickster
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.04,0:21:11.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是怒火船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:11.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Captain Mag
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.79,0:21:13.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:13.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ma
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来该我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's up to me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.21,0:21:23.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我隐形起来溜过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:23.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just sneak over, unseen
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后捉他们个措手不及
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and catch them by surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(732.084,763)}悬崖危险
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.10,0:21:35.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弄下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:35.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get it off
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.78,0:21:43.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:43.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glad that's over
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.92,0:21:51.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.92,0:21:51.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.54,0:21:52.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了  我们赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:52.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we did it, we won
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.45,0:21:56.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这成功之日属于邪恶帮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:56.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This day belongs to EVIL
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.88,0:22:03.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你输了  美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:03.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've lost, Mermaidman
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.38,0:22:06.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根据超级英雄与超级恶人的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:06.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the superhero- super-villain rules say
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.38,0:22:09.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你必须要答应我的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:09.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you have to give in to my demands
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行  你想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, what do you want?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.66,0:22:12.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,统治世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:12.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,World domination
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.81,0:22:14.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟他说我们要统治世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:14.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell him we want world domination
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.90,0:22:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要让他吃土
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'll make him eat dirt
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.06,0:22:21.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先还是要统治世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:21.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In addition to the domination thing
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.19,0:22:24.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一  把我当作超级英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:24.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Number one: I want to be treated like a superhero
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.40,0:22:25.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别把我当小跟班
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:25.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not a sidekick
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.94,0:22:29.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二  要叫我企鹅男人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:29.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Number two: I want to be called Barnacleman
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.91,0:22:31.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第三
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:31.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And number three
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.41,0:22:34.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说啊  统治世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:34.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, domination
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.33,0:22:35.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要成人尺寸的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:35.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want an adult-sized Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.71,0:22:39.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有听见他说吃土吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:39.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you hear him say anything about eating dirt?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.08,0:22:40.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要搭把手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:40.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Need a hand?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.83,0:22:41.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超级搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:41.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Super pal?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:49.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(703.965,776.999)}朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.26,0:22:52.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴你又回归正义一方了  凯尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:52.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good to have you back on the side of justice, Kyle
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.31,0:22:55.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给你买蟹黄堡去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:55.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go get you that Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.82,0:22:57.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然就这
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.82,0:22:57.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was that it?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.44,0:22:59.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:22:59.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel sick
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.98,0:23:01.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这倒让我想起了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:01.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This reminds me of the time
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.02,0:23:03.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟大虾杀手去墨西哥旅游城市坎昆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.01,0:23:03.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I went to Cancún with the Killer Shrimp
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.92,0:23:05.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边有木瓜饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.92,0:23:05.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They had these papaya drinks
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.01,0:23:06.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的海神王啊  闭嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.01,0:23:06.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Neptune, shut up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.53,0:23:09.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(392.655,488.999)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.32,0:23:15.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这成人尺寸的蟹黄堡吃得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:15.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's that adult-sized Krabby Patty treating you
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.46,0:23:16.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,企鹅男
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:16.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacle
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.76,0:23:17.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:17.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,man?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:18.12,0:23:19.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说实在的  太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:19.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's pretty big
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.37,0:23:22.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不清楚吃不吃得完
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.37,0:23:22.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I can finish the whole thing
